data.description: You won't want to miss the opportunity to own this beautiful four bedroom 3 bathroom home in the highly desirable Wolf Branch School system.  This beauty sits on an expansive cul-de-sac and provides tons of curb appeal.  This home is loaded with hardwood floors, vaulted ceilings, fresh paint throughout! Enjoy an open floor plan with hearth room, office space, laundry room and so much more!  The primary bedroom suite features large walk in closet, vaulted ceilings, corner garden tub and separate shower.  So many rooms available not to mention a large unfinished basement waiting for just more rooms!  Two egress windows, rough in bathroom, sump pump, and 9 foot tall ceilings will make a beautiful addition to the home.  So many great financing options available so marry the house and date the rate!
